00:16:18,961 --> 00:16:20,223
Pozdrav. Gđo. C.

238
00:16:20,396 --> 00:16:21,863
Rich, ne zovi me Gđa. C,
ozbiljna sam.

239
00:16:22,031 --> 00:16:24,625
Silazi sa radne površine.
Oh.

240
00:16:24,800 --> 00:16:26,631
Denis Petey Cooverman,
pogledaj se.

241
00:16:26,802 --> 00:16:28,099
Izgledaš slatko.

242
00:16:28,570 --> 00:16:30,504
Super slatko.

243
00:16:30,673 --> 00:16:31,697
Ne misli ona tako.

244
00:16:31,874 --> 00:16:33,102
Izgledaš dobro.
Izgledaš cool.

245
00:16:33,275 --> 00:16:34,299
Da.

246
00:16:34,476 --> 00:16:38,173
Samo trebao bi malo spustiti
struk na tim hlačama.

247
00:16:38,347 --> 00:16:40,747
Oh, ne nosiš te užasne gaće.

248
00:16:40,916 --> 00:16:42,042
Mama. Bože.

249
00:16:42,217 --> 00:16:44,082
Moram ti se složiti s mamom...

250
00:16:44,253 --> 00:16:46,585
