281
00:18:10,506 --> 00:18:12,872
to je relativno nova stvar.

282
00:18:13,041 --> 00:18:15,407
Smislili su to u pedesetima....

283
00:18:15,577 --> 00:18:17,943
Uredu je zabaviti se ponekad.

284
00:18:18,113 --> 00:18:21,412
