"Koji K."

285
00:18:21,583 --> 00:18:24,245
Curtis Armstrong, Risky Business,
1983, Paul Brickman.

286
00:18:24,419 --> 00:18:29,118
Osim što on nije rekao " K,"
rekao je " Kurac."

287
00:18:31,493 --> 00:18:34,360
Znaš što mislim.
Carpe diem.

288
00:18:34,530 --> 00:18:37,897
Nisam znao da ste toliki ljubitelj
fimova G. C.

289
00:18:38,066 --> 00:18:39,727
Robin Williams u
Društvu mrtvih pjesnika.

290
00:18:39,902 --> 00:18:44,430
Da, hvala. Hvala, Rich.
Znamo. Odlično je.

291
00:18:44,606 --> 00:18:46,267
Dođi ovamo, molim.

292
00:18:51,013 --> 00:18:55,712
Imate kondome u mom ormariću
kraj kreveta.

293
00:18:58,287 --> 00:19:01,814
Znate li točno, koliko ih ima?

294
00:19:02,991 --> 00:19:06,950
Nisu igračke.

295
00:19:09,298 --> 00:19:11,459
