328
00:21:22,164 --> 00:21:23,290
Što?

329
00:21:23,465 --> 00:21:24,955
Ne. Ne...ne.

330
00:21:27,069 --> 00:21:31,028
Hej, daj, ti debela? Zašto bi to rekao?
Nije retardiran.

331
00:21:31,206 --> 00:21:33,037
Moj brat je retardiran.

332
00:21:41,416 --> 00:21:43,475
To je...toj je bilo....hladno.

333
00:21:43,652 --> 00:21:45,415
Sigurno nemaš ni brata.

334
00:21:45,587 --> 00:21:47,316
Ne, on je..uh...umro.

335
00:21:49,624 --> 00:21:53,355
Da, to je stvarno...
Prešla si me, to je....

336
00:22:02,904 --> 00:22:05,338
Žao mi je.

337
