00:25:21,870 --> 00:25:23,565
Smiješan si.

394
00:25:25,941 --> 00:25:27,272
Kako se osjećaš?

395
00:25:35,083 --> 00:25:36,914
Prilično dobro, pretpostavljam.

396
00:25:55,003 --> 00:25:57,096
