00:26:32,841 --> 00:26:35,071
Oh, vino me podsjeća na Isusa.

411
00:26:35,243 --> 00:26:37,108
Znaš li što, Denis,
stvarno moramo ići.

412
00:26:37,279 --> 00:26:39,247
Inače, bila je dobra zabava.

413
00:26:52,027 --> 00:26:53,756
Oh, sranje, Kevin.

414
00:26:53,928 --> 00:26:55,657
