415
00:26:59,467 --> 00:27:01,435
Trebati ćemo više vafli.

416
00:27:13,815 --> 00:27:16,079
Sean, ti zločesti dečko.

417
00:27:18,453 --> 00:27:19,818
Ne, ne, ne, ne.

418
00:27:22,624 --> 00:27:24,922
