433
00:28:19,781 --> 00:28:21,646
Jesi li se drogirao?

434
00:28:21,816 --> 00:28:23,340
Ne sada, Lisbee.

435
00:28:23,518 --> 00:28:24,542
Nafiksao se?

436
00:28:24,719 --> 00:28:27,654
